EXRIPARIAN: Landfire EVT reclassified into a binary raster where non-riparian cells are 0 and riparian cells are 1.
HISTRIPARIAN: Landfire BpS reclassified into a binary raster where non-riparian cells are 0 and riparian cells are 1.
EXVEGETATED: Landfire EVT reclassified into a binary raster where non-vegetated cells are 0 and vegetated cells are 1.
HISTVEGETATED: Landfire BpS reclassified into a binary raster where non-vegetated cells are 0 and vegetated cells are 1.
CONVERSION: Integer raster where each value represents a conversion from one vegetation type to another between EVT and BpS Landfire rasters.
D8FLOWDIR: D8 Flow directions calculated using TauDEM from input pitfilled DEM.
FPACCESS: Floodplain accessibility raster where inaccessible areas are 0 and accessible areas are 1.
GEOM_POINTS: Integrated Geographic Objects - Points placed at a specified distance interval along the valley centerline. This distance is a function of the average valley width for a given stream.
IGOS: IGOs attributed with values for rcat analyses calculated within a single DGO or an aggregation of DGOs.
GEOM_LINES: NHD Flowlines intersected with land ownership, road and rail.
REACHES: NHD Flowlines attributed with values for rcat analyses.
GEOM_DGOS: Discrete Geographic Objects - The valley bottom split into a sampling frame of polygons where the IGO points are at the center of each polygon.
DGOS: DGOs attributed with values for rcat analyses within the DGO extent.
